Job Description	Gen AI Research: The role focuses on long form content generation and localization, including refining how large language models interact with knowledge graphs and implementing fine tuning techniques such as RLHF and LoRA to improve cultural and linguistic accuracy. They will collaborate with the Machine Translation and LLM teams on applied R&D experiments, under the mentorship of senior research scientists

Gen AI Development: The role focuses on building and scaling Copilot features for content creation and operational workflows, alongside expanding Text to Speech capabilities across multiple languages. Selected candidates will work on improving TTS quality and scale for European languages including German, French, Spanish, Italian, and Portuguese, as well as Indian regional languages such as Tamil, Telugu, Malayalam, Kannada, and Marathi, under the guidance of senior engineering and research teams. 

Growth: The role sits at the intersection of analytics, product, and growth, tackling first-of-their-kind challenges across content, revenue, and user acquisition. Selected candidates will work on problem statements spanning content growth and expansion, revenue and retention optimisation, AI driven production and scaling, content adaptation and commissioning, and live action content strategy, contributing to measurable outcomes across diverse genres and markets. The role demands strong analytical thinking, an action oriented mindset, and the ability to break complex problems into practical, executable solutions, working closely with cross functional teams across creative, product, and marketing
About the Company	Pocket FM is a leading AI-powered audio series platform with 250M+ listeners, 300,000+ creators, and 100,000+ audio series, streaming over 140 billion minutes annually. Having crossed $400M ARR, we are one of the fastest-growing media-tech companies globally and the first Indian B2C product to achieve sustained success across the US, Europe, and beyond. At our core, we use Generative AI to reinvent how audio entertainment is created, localized, and consumed. Our GenAI teams build large-scale systems across content generation, voice AI, multilingual localization, creator copilots, and agentic workflows, solving for how stories can be created, adapted, and enjoyed globally while preserving creativity and quality. We operate at the intersection of AI, entertainment, and consumer scale, with work that ships fast and impacts millions of end users directly
